<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ ěr biān shì fǒu yǒu jǐng zhōng zhǎng míng 迦南333</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ ěr biān shì fǒu yǒu jǐng zhōng zhǎng míng, xīn zhōng shì fǒu yǐ àn dàn le kuān guǎng xīn xiōng.
 shēn yè lǐ yǒu méi yǒu nǐ de qí dǎo shēng, hé chǎng shàng yǒu méi yǒu nǐ de shēn yǐng?
 dōu wàng jì dì xiōng suǒ yǒu de cuò, zhǔ zǎo yǐ yòng ài yě bǎ nǐ bāo róng.
 dōu zài zǒu lù shì yī yàng de chén zhòng, yī yàng yǒu fēng yǔ yī yàng yǒu cǎi hóng.
 yé sū wèi nǐ shí jià shàng bèi dīng, yé sū wèi nǐ shòu jǐn qī líng.
 zhǔ nèi tóng gōng zhǔ nèi tóng gōng, zǒng yào zhēng kāi nǐ xìn xīn de yǎn jīng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>333</hymn_number>
</song>